line_1: Let not ignoble Fires your Youth mislead,
line_2: With equal Fortune grace your Nuptial Bed;

line_1: Cannot compel, him Pride cannot mislead
line_2: Him Fashion cannot tempt, him abject Need

line_1: To guard good Kings, and Tyrants to mislead,
line_2: Drunk with Prerogative, which Fate decreed
